{"title":"Linux 日常管理","slug":"Linux-日常管理","date":"2018-07-18T03:02:10.000Z","updated":"2018-07-18T04:09:46.561Z","comments":true,"excerpt":"","content":"<blockquote><p>But what I want to say is that even if you fully master it, you can’t be a qualified Linux system administrator now. After all, the system administrator will do too much.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">w</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#查看当前系统的负载,关注的应该是第一行中的 ‘load average:’ 后面的三个数值。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#第一个数值表示1分钟内系统的平均负载值；</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#第二个数值表示5分钟内系统的平均负载值；第三个数值表示15分钟系统的平均负载值。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">cat /proc/cpuinfo</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#查看服务器有几个cpu</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">vmstat </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#监控系统的状态</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">top </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#显示进程所占系统资源 l t m</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">sar</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#监控系统状态</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#sar -n DEV 查看网卡流量 </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#sar -n DEV 1 5 时时查看网卡流量呢</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#sar -n DEV -f /var/log/sa/sa24 查看某一天的网卡流量ps  -elf</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">nload ens33</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#实时查看网卡流量</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">free</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#查看内存使用状况</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#可以加-m 或者-g选项分别以M或G为单位打印内存使用状况</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">ps</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#ps aux  &amp;  ps  -elf</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#kill  -9  进程pid</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">netstat </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#查看网络状况</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#netstat -lnp （打印当前系统启动哪些端口）以及 netstat  -an （打印网络连接状况）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">tcpdump</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#抓包工具</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">df -h</span><br><span class=\"line\">du -sh</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#统计分区、文件大小</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">fdisk -l</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#列出磁盘设备与分区大小</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">/var/<span class=\"built_in\">log</span>/messages</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#Linux 系统日志</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">dmesg</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#显示系统的启动信息</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Linux","path":"api/tags/Linux.json"}]}